- page_title 'Login'
%section
  .page-header
    %h1
      Login
      %small So we know where to guide you :-)

  .row
    .span8
      .page-header
        %h3 With credentials
      = semantic_form_for :user_session, :url => user_session_path do |f|

        = f.inputs do
          = f.input :email
          = f.input :password
          = f.input :remember_me, :as => :boolean

        = f.actions
    .span8
      .page-header
        %h3 Don't have an account yet?
      %p
        = link_to 'Registering', signup_path
        an account enables you to create your personal tv guide. This will be a collection of all your favorite tv programs.
